comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:20.001Z",codex-root,pm init created repository-local storage and installed twelve bundled packages.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:20.001Z",codex-root,Never edit PM TOON or JSONL stores directly; use PM commands for every mutation.
learnings[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:20.001Z",codex-root,Explicit --workspace binding prevents accidental mutation of the global tracker.
  "2026-07-16T17:10:59.356Z",codex-root,PM linked-test tracker context clones tracker state but not the full repository file tree. Run history checks in linked-test tracker mode and run check-files against the live workspace.
  "2026-07-16T17:13:32.134Z",codex-root,A root-wide settings.json credential ignore also hides .agents/pm/settings.json. Preserve credential hygiene with a narrow PM settings negation so repository-local governance is reproducible.
